column4: Name of the preferred contact on your new client
Email of the preferred contact on your new client.
Phone number of the preferred contact on your new client.
Mobile Phone number of the preferred contact on your new client.
Client name, normally used for a company name.
Client code, your specific code for the client.
Client email address. Must be a valid email address ex: foo@bar.com
Client language. May be en, pt or es; defaults to the account language.
Client’s postal code for it’s company address.
Country, normally used for a company country. Although country is optional, when supplied, it should match one of the country list on the Appendix of this Documentation
The client fiscal ID (Número de Contribuinte)
Default observations for the client, the text in here will be added to the observations field of all the invoices sent to this client.
Send options for the client. Available options are: 1 - send only the original document / 2 – the original and duplicate / 3 – the original, duplicate and triplicate. These affect the generated pdf.
